OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FA Guernsey politician is asking if
OL,8,Fthere is enough scrutiny of the
OL,9,Fisland's maternity services.
OL,11,FIt follows a damning 2015 report
OL,12,Fwritten by Dr Elaine Maxwell following
OL,13,Fthe death of a child the year before.
OL,15,FThe report set out set out 12
OL,16,Frecommendations on how the maternity
OL,17,Fservice could improve and led to
OL,18,Fmonitoring visits from the Nursing and
OL,19,FMidwifery Council (NMC).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FHowever, the public has never been
OL,8,Fmade aware of how those
OL,9,Frecommendations were used or met.
OL,11,FITV News now understands that those
OL,12,Frecommendations ranged from grading
OL,13,Funexpected events by consequence to
OL,14,Fintroducing trained investigators into
OL,15,Fthe health department.
OL,17,FDeputy Gavin St Pier wants further
OL,18,Fclarity on how those recommendations
OL,19,Fwere met, adding that recent responses
OL,20,Ffrom the Committee for Health and
OL,21,FSocial Care (HSC) are "disappointing".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FHe told ITV News: "It would just be
OL,8,Fhelpful to be a little bit more
OL,9,Ftransparent, open, and honest."
OL,11,FEarlier this month, Deputy Gavin St
OL,12,FPier wrote to HSC to ask what action
OL,13,Fthe Committee had taken in response to
OL,14,FDr Maxwell's recommendations.
OL,16,FDeputy Dr George Oswald, the President
OL,17,Fof HSC, responded that while all
OL,18,Fpoints from Dr Maxwell's report were
OL,19,Faddressed, they were unable to provide
OL,20,Fa "recommendation-by-recommendation
OL,21,Faccount of actions".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FDeputy Oswald's response reads: "The
OL,8,FDepartment's own action plan from 2015
OL,9,Fdemonstrates that work was initiated
OL,10,Facross all 12 recommendations and an
OL,11,Fupdate provided to the then Committee
OL,12,Fin 2017 confirms that all actions were
OL,13,Fcompleted.
OL,15,F"Since that time, maternity services
OL,16,Fhave undergone significant further
OL,17,Fdevelopment and have continued to
OL,18,Fevolve in line with UK standards,
OL,19,Fnational guidance and subsequent
OL,20,Freviews.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,F"The Committee is satisfied that the
OL,8,Ffindings of the 2015 review have long
OL,9,Fsince been overtaken by subsequent
OL,10,Fservice improvements, national
OL,11,Fstandards and ongoing quality
OL,12,Fassurance processes."
OL,14,FDeputy St Pier says the HSC response
OL,15,Fis "disappointing".
OL,17,F"The questions weren't particularly
OL,18,Fdifficult," the Guernsey politician
OL,19,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,F"I will engage with the committee, and
OL,8,FI do hope that they will will
OL,9,Freconsider the response they've given
OL,10,Fand perhaps provide something a little
OL,11,Fmore useful.
OL,13,F"I absolutely understand that,
OL,14,Fparticularly in Health and Care, there
OL,15,Fis a desire to reassure the public,
OL,16,Fbut when it comes to accountability
OL,17,Fand transparency, I think it is
OL,18,Fimportant that there is honesty and
OL,19,Frealism.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,F"The reality is that in any service,
OL,8,Fthere will always be some issues and
OL,9,Fchallenges. So let's just face up to
OL,10,Fit and deal with them."
OL,12,FHealth bosses have now responded to
OL,13,FDeputy St Pier's concerns, but they
OL,14,Fare essentially just doubling down on
OL,15,Ftheir original response.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FDeputy George Oswald said on Thursday
OL,8,Fafternoon (23 June) that he would not
OL,9,Fwant the publication of historical
OL,10,Finformation to cause unnecessary alarm
OL,11,For anxiety for expectant mothers and
OL,12,Ftheir families.
OL,14,FHe also said that he would not want to
OL,15,Fdiminish the sad circumstances of the
OL,16,Fcase itself, no matter when it
OL,17,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FThe President of HSC states: "(The
OL,8,Freport) relates to a deeply
OL,9,Fregrettable and tragic case. However,
OL,10,Fit occurred more than a decade ago,
OL,11,Fand maternity services have changed
OL,12,Fsignificantly since that time.
OL,14,F"Since the review, I am confident that
OL,15,Fmaternity services are very different,
OL,16,Fwith strengthened clinical leadership,
OL,17,Fenhanced staffing levels, improved
OL,18,Fgovernance arrangements and ongoing
OL,19,Fquality assurance processes.
OL,26,@oD@_pmpD@Gpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784917111
OL,3,CCalls for transparency on maternity
OL,4,Cprogress following previous death of
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,F"These changes have helped to ensure
OL,8,Fthat the service continues to evolve
OL,9,Fand respond to emerging best practice."
OL,11,FSo the President of Health is
OL,12,Fconfident in the services provided.
OL,14,FStill, they will not give Deputy St
OL,15,FPier the information he wants: a
OL,16,Fbreakdown of the recommendations and
OL,17,Fhow exactly they were met.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/10
